 * @component_start
 * code: faq
 * name: 常见问题
 * name_en: FAQ
 * description: Roulette Supernova FAQ rebuilt as a two-column inline accordion so each column opens independently.
 * category: content
 * region: content
 * @component_end
 *
 * @fields_start
 *
 * group:display => 显示控制
 * display.show_section => 显示此区域:select:yes|yes,no
 * display.show_title => 显示标题:select:yes|yes,no
 * display.show_intro => 显示简介:select:yes|yes,no
 * display.first_open => 首个问题默认展开:select:no|yes,no
 *
 * group:style => 样式配置
 * style.bg_color => 背景主色:color:#1b0910
 * style.accent_color => 强调色:color:#dfff5a
 * style.title_color => 标题颜色:color:#f7f1e8
 * style.text_color => 正文颜色:color:#cbbcae
 * style.panel_bg_color => 卡片背景色:color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06)
 * style.card_border_color => 卡片边框色:color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)
 * style.card_radius => 卡片圆角:number:24|px
 * style.section_padding => 区域内边距(PC端):number:72|px
 * style.section_padding_mobile => 区域内边距(移动端):number:48|px
 *
 * group:texts => 文本内容
 * texts.badge => 徽标文字:text:Roulette Support
 * texts.title => 区域标题:text:Frequently Asked Questions
 * texts.intro => 简介:textarea:Open any roulette question inline to compare table flow, mobile readability, and support paths without leaving the section.
 * texts.tag_1 => 标签1:text:Fast Join
 * texts.tag_2 => 标签2:text:Live Wheel
 * texts.tag_3 => 标签3:text:Mobile Ready
 * texts.faq_1_question => 问题1:text:How do I choose the right roulette table here?
 * texts.faq_1_answer => 答案1:textarea:Start with the table labels and short descriptions. Faster rooms suit short sessions, while steadier rooms are better if you want more time to read the wheel and bets.
 * texts.faq_2_question => 问题2:text:Does Roulette Supernova work well on mobile?
 * texts.faq_2_answer => 答案2:textarea:Yes. The key wheel view, table buttons, and support sections are arranged to stay readable on smaller screens without awkward overflow.
 * texts.faq_3_question => 问题3:text:Can I move between live and classic roulette rooms quickly?
 * texts.faq_3_answer => 答案3:textarea:Yes. The homepage keeps table switching direct, so you can compare room styles and move into another roulette lane without digging through clutter.
 * texts.faq_4_question => 问题4:text:Are the bet zones easy to read for new players?
 * texts.faq_4_answer => 答案4:textarea:Yes. Contrast is kept strong so straight bets, color bets, and common roulette actions remain easy to scan before you join.
 * texts.faq_5_question => 问题5:text:Do the quick-entry buttons take me straight to the room list?
 * texts.faq_5_answer => 答案5:textarea:Yes. Primary actions are placed close to the table descriptions so the route from homepage to roulette room stays short and obvious.
 * texts.faq_6_question => 问题6:text:Where can I find help if I get stuck on a table?
 * texts.faq_6_answer => 答案6:textarea:Use the support and contact areas linked across the site. They stay easy to reach from the main navigation and footer.
 *
 * @fields_end
